fucksocks.server

Class GenericSocksProxyServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • fucksocks.server.GenericSocksProxyServer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SocksProxyServer, Runnable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SSLSocksProxyServer

    public class GenericSocksProxyServer
extends Object
implements SocksProxyServer, Runnable
    The class GenericSocksProxyServer is a implementation of SocksProxyServer.
    You can create a SOKCS5 server easily by following codes:
     ProxyServer proxyServer = new GenericSocksProxyServer(Socks5Handler.class);
 proxyServer.start(); // Create a SOCKS5 server bind at 1080.
    If you want change the port, you can using following codes: 
     proxyServer.start(9999);
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Youchao Feng
    date
    Apr 19, 2015 1:10:17 PM
